pageContext.claim: “Every day we are living by our motto, promises made, promises kept. And some of the fake news -- and they know, they say that I made promises and I actually kept more promises than I made. I think we've done more than we've even said.”
pageContext.analysis: According to our Trump Promise Tracker, Trump has kept 23 percent of 60 key promises and broken 27 percent; many others remain unfulfilled.
